title: The World's Most Expensive Cigars
itunes:title: The World's Most Expensive Cigars
description:
This week The Cigar Authority takes a look at some of the world's most expensive cigars. We also update the FDA News and take a look at cigars that just missed being a contender for Cigar of the Year and we smoke our top Limited Edition cigars from 2014. 
We also break down the latest issue of Cigar Journal magazine!

We have Cigar News, Cigar Trademarks, Old Fart Freddy, Debonaire and go inside the Asylum
